Package: unace-nonfree
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: extract, test and view .ace archives (non-free version)
 The unace utility is used for extracting, testing and viewing the contents of
 archives created with the ACE archiver.
 .
 Unlike the unace package which can only extract ACE 1.0 archives, the
 unace-nonfree package allows one to unpack all current ACE archives.
